The returned string is empty when the user cancels the dialog. The initial directory parameter is connected to the JC Lib folder browser.

Previous workflow example retained from the original Qt pack:

```cpp
const QString fileName = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(
    this,
    tr("Open configuration"),
