```

Returns an empty QStringList when canceled.

Previous workflow example retained from the original Qt pack:

```cpp
const QStringList files = QFileDialog::getOpenFileNames(
    this,
    tr("Select log files"),
    QDir::homePath(),
    tr("Log files (*.log *.txt);;All files (*)"));

for (const QString &fileName : files)
{
